{"tid":1856342,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"三日兩夜 簡淑兒 陳婉衡","createTime":"2020-02-01T14:35:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-15T15:01:14.000Z","uid":38456,"like":3,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"b763afef86bf165d05aca2e960f912fa075b895b","tid":1856342,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T14:35:28.000Z","msg":"3日2夜[粵]&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n簡淑兒、陳婉衡遠赴英國北愛爾蘭細味歷史，必到貝爾法斯特地標經典郵輪紀念館，以及依據郵輪藍本建造的酒店，回味驚世傳奇。再往船艙餐廳品味下午茶，重溫電影浪漫足跡。來趟叢林探險，單聽淑兒穿梭樹林的超高分貝聲量，已感受到無限刺激！考膽量第二波的室內跳傘，無論任何天氣，都可挑戰極限！兩位吃貨出動，反轉當地市場「掃街」。二人還忽發奇想，要DIY有溫度的糖果手信。她們怎會錯過當地夜生活？手調特飲至夠Chill！"},{"pid":"920f09331c8653bf5900cf4d8c4b43d44359c14b","tid":1856342,"uid":201751,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T14:37:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />TVB"},{"pid":"452cdbb43f25d1c841161e90c1940815606834f9","tid":1856342,"uid":130105,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T14:41:21.000Z","msg":"陳婉衡真係胸大遮三醜嘅人版<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b90490f18ab10134186851696970642a698a3067","tid":1856342,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T14:55:18.000Z","msg":"no body"},{"pid":"d953924eeaebf58ffe7fa9d0ec93303d8df449f7","tid":1856342,"uid":155818,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"452cdbb43f25d1c841161e90c1940815606834f9","tid":1856342,"uid":130105,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T14:41:21.000Z","msg":"陳婉衡真係胸大遮三醜嘅人版<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/sosad.gif\" cl